Dataset: Global Store Operations | Reporting Period: 2011 - 2014

1. Financial Highlights
•	Revenue Performance: Dashboard total sales $12.62M reflect kar raha hai, jismein year-over-year steady growth dekhi gayi hai.
•	Profitability: Total profit $1.46M hai, jismein Technology category ka contribution sabse zyada ($0.66M) hai, jo high-margin sales ko indicate karta hai.
•	Efficiency: Average delivery time 3.97 days hai, jo industry standards ke hisaab se kaafi competitive hai.

2. Operational Insights
•	Top Performing Category: Sales aur Profit dono mein Technology lead kar raha hai, jabki Furniture segment mein profit margins thode kam hain ($0.28M), jo high shipping costs ya low-price points ki wajah se ho sakta hai.
•	Logistics Efficiency: Majority orders Standard Delivery ke through ship ho rahe hain. "On-Time Critical" aur "Delayed Critical" orders ka volume kam hai, jo ek stable supply chain system ko darshata hai.
•	Trend Analysis: Year-wise sales trend se pata chalta hai ki business scale ho raha hai, khaaskar 2013-2014 ke beech mein sharp revenue jump dekha gaya hai.

3. Strategic Recommendations (MNC-Level Advice)
•	Profit Optimization: Furniture category mein margins badhane ke liye operational costs ko review karne ki zarurat hai.
•	Delivery Strategy: "Standard Delivery" par heavy reliance hai; premium shipping options (Same-day/Express) ko promote karke extra revenue generate kiya ja sakta hai.
•	Target Marketing: Technology segment ki success ko dekhte hue, high-value tech products par marketing spend badhaya ja sakta hai.
